HR 319 Original 2026 Regular Session Sawyer
Requests the actuary for the legislative auditor, in consultation with the actuaries for the
Firefighters' Retirement System (FRS) and the Baton Rouge City Parish Employees'
Retirement System (CPERS), to perform the actuarial investigation required by present law
and to report findings relative to the cost and feasibility of merging firefighters from CPERS
into FRS.
